The paper discusses natural language processing (NLP) tasks and proposes a way to learn useful representations from natural language annotations in the format of question-answering (QA). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on NLP and related tasks. The paper also mentions using modern language models, which suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions improving on a wide range of tasks, which could include tasks related to neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV).
